Re-add the codeWeb entry point to the web build

Adds buildfile.codeWeb back to the vscodeWebEntryPoints array in the
web gulp build file, ensuring the workbench code is included in the
web-embedded distribution.

Index: code-editor-src/build/gulpfile.vscode.web.ts
===================================================================
--- code-editor-src.orig/build/gulpfile.vscode.web.ts
+++ code-editor-src/build/gulpfile.vscode.web.ts
@@ -115,6 +115,7 @@ const vscodeWebEntryPoints = [
 	buildfile.workerBackgroundTokenization,
 	buildfile.keyboardMaps,
 	buildfile.workbenchWeb,
+	buildfile.codeWeb,
 ].flat();
 
